## Introduction 👋

[Epic 免费人](https://github.com/QIN2DIM/epic-awesome-gamer) 帮助玩家优雅地领取免费游戏。内置 [hcaptcha-challenger](https://github.com/QIN2DIM/hcaptcha-challenger) AI 模块，直面人机挑战。

